==Old English==
===Etymology===
From Germanic ''*khauzjianan''.  Cognate with Old Saxon [[horian|hōrian]] (Dutch [[hooren]]), Old High German [[horen|hōren]] (German [[hören]]), Old Norse [[heyra]] (Swedish [[höra]]), Gothic [[𐌷𐌰𐌿𐍃𐌾𐌰𐌽]].

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/'hy:ran/}}

