(ġe){{Unicode|'''hȳran'''}} (class 1 weak: ''3 singular present'' {{Unicode|'''[[hyreþ|hȳreþ]]'''}}, ''3 singular preterite'' {{Unicode|'''[[hyrde|hȳrde]]'''}}, ''preterite plural'' {{Unicode|'''[[hyrdon|hȳrdon]]'''}}, ''past participle'' (ġe){{Unicode|'''[[hyred|hȳred]]'''}})
